 five practical strategies that reap has employed to maximize the effectiveness of our impact evaluations these strategies include the use of randomization and other experimental and quasi experimental research designs pursuit of local and international collaboration strict attention to policy relevance a modular incremental research approach and robust outreach download pdf+ complete modified february 2011 pdf 212_ _3ie_experience_paper pdf 257.8 kb topics china stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
